{"image_id": "KEY_2015_page_223", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "18. Long-Term Debt", "bbox": [528.1, 159.8, 746.9, 184.8]}, {"text": "The following table presents the components of our long-term debt, net of unamortized discounts and", "bbox": [162.5, 207.1, 1009.4, 227.9]}, {"text": "adjustments related to hedging with derivative financial instruments. We use interest rate swaps and caps, which", "bbox": [162.5, 232.1, 1101.1, 252.9]}, {"text": "modify the repricing characteristics of certain long-term debt, to manage interest rate risk. For more information", "bbox": [162.5, 257.1, 1100.1, 277.9]}, {"text": "about such financial instruments, see Note 8 (“Derivatives and Hedging Activities”).", "bbox": [162.5, 282.1, 869.4, 302.9]}, {"text": "December 31,", "bbox": [162.5, 320.6, 259.7, 337.3]}, {"text": "dollars in millions", "bbox": [162.5, 349.8, 284.5, 366.5]}, {"text": "2015", "bbox": [987.5, 349.8, 1020.8, 366.5]}, {"text": "2014", "bbox": [1070.8, 349.8, 1104.2, 366.5]}, {"text": "Senior medium-term notes due through 2021 (a)", "bbox": [162.5, 377.0, 477.7, 393.7]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [958.3, 376.9, 966.7, 393.5]}, {"text": "2,819", "bbox": [983.3, 376.9, 1020.8, 393.5]}, {"text": "$ 2,575", "bbox": [1050.0, 377.0, 1104.2, 393.7]}, {"text": "1.066% Subordinated notes due 2028 (b)", "bbox": [162.5, 397.9, 428.6, 414.5]}, {"text": "162", "bbox": [995.8, 397.7, 1020.8, 414.4]}, {"text": "162", "bbox": [1079.2, 397.9, 1104.2, 414.5]}, {"text": "6.875% Subordinated notes due 2029 (b)", "bbox": [162.5, 418.7, 428.6, 435.4]}, {"text": "114", "bbox": [995.8, 418.5, 1020.8, 435.2]}, {"text": "113", "bbox": [1079.2, 418.7, 1104.2, 435.4]}, {"text": "7.750% Subordinated notes due 2029 (b)", "bbox": [162.5, 439.5, 428.6, 456.2]}, {"text": "147", "bbox": [995.8, 439.4, 1020.8, 456.0]}, {"text": "147", "bbox": [1079.2, 439.5, 1104.2, 456.2]}, {"text": "Total parent company", "bbox": [195.8, 466.6, 341.9, 483.3]}, {"text": "3,242", "bbox": [983.3, 466.5,