otes. These notes may be redeemed", "bbox": [195.8, 974.0, 1081.9, 990.7]}, {"text": "prior to their maturity date.", "bbox": [195.8, 994.9, 376.3, 1011.5]}, {"text": "(e)", "bbox": [162.5, 1025.1, 181.0, 1041.7]}, {"text": "These notes are all obligations of KeyBank and may not be redeemed prior to their maturity dates.", "bbox": [195.8, 1025.1, 849.7, 1041.7]}, {"text": "(f)", "bbox": [162.5, 1055.3, 179.2, 1071.9]}, {"text": "The secured borrowing had weighted-average interest rates of 4.42% at December 31, 2015, and 4.41% at December 31, 2014. This", "bbox": [195.8, 1055.3, 1074.9, 1071.9]}, {"text": "borrowing is collateralized by commercial lease financing receivables, and principal reductions are based on the cash payments received", "bbox": [195.8, 1076.1, 1104.1, 1092.8]}, {"text": "from the related receivables. Additional information pertaining to these commercial lease financing receivables is included in Note 4", "bbox": [195.8, 1096.9, 1078.8, 1113.6]}, {"text": "(“Loans and Loans Held for Sale”).", "bbox": [195.8, 1117.8, 432.7, 1134.4]}, {"text": "(g)", "bbox": [162.5, 1148.0, 181.9, 1164.6]}, {"text": "Long-term advances from the Federal Home Loan Bank had a weighted-average interest rate of 3.58% at December 31, 2015, and 3.47%", "bbox": [195.8, 1148.0, 1110.4, 1164.6]}, {"text": "at December 31, 2014. These advances, which had fixed interest rates, were secured by real estate loans and securities totaling $251", "bbox": [195.8, 1168.8, 1074.8, 1185.5]}, {"text": "million at December 31, 2015, and $280 million at December 31, 2014.", "bbox": [195.8, 1189.6, 672.4, 1206.3]}, {"text": "(h)", "bbox": [162.5, 1219.9, 181.9, 1236.5]}, {"text": "Investment Fund Financing had a weighted-average interest rate of 1.94% at December 31, 2015, and 2.01% December 31, 2014.", "bbox": [195.8, 1219.9, 1058.6, 1236.5]}, {"text": "At December 31, 2015, scheduled principal payments on long-term debt were as follows:", "bbox": [162.5, 1260.5, 907.6, 1281.4]}, {"text": 